  "text": "The value of the sound wavelength for the formation of light wave reflection generally corresponds to the Bragg grating period [CITATION_1] . In this case, the wavelength of the reflected light will differ from the resonant wavelength of the Bragg grating due to the Doppler effect from the moving sound wave.",
